I"ê<h2 id="web-scenario">Web Scenario</h2>
<p>To monitor a website in <strong>Zabbix</strong>, a new <em>web scenario</em> has to be created.</p>

<ol>
  <li>Navigate to <em>Configuration</em> &gt; <em>Hosts</em> &gt; Select host for web monitoring</li>
  <li>Go to the <strong>Web scenarios</strong> tab and click on <em>Create web scenario</em>.</li>
  <li><strong>Scenario</strong>:
<img src="/files/zabbix-website-monitoring/scenario.png" alt="scenario.png" />
    <ul>
      <li><em>Name</em>: <code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;$WEBSITE_TITLE&gt;</code></li>
      <li><em>Application</em> OR <em>New application</em>: <code class="highlighter-rouge">HTTP</code></li>
      <li><em>Enabled</em>:</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Steps</strong>:
<img src="/files/zabbix-website-monitoring/steps.png" alt="steps.png" />
    <ul>
      <li><em>Name</em>: <code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;$WEBSITE_TITLE&gt;</code></li>
      <li><em>URL</em>: <code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;$WEBSITE_URL&gt;</code></li>
      <li><em>Follow redirects</em>: <code class="highlighter-rouge">x</code></li>
      <li><em>Retrieve only headers</em>: <code class="highlighter-rouge">x</code></li>
      <li><em>Required status codes</em>: <code class="highlighter-rouge">200</code></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Click <em>Add</em>.</li>
</ol>

<h2 id="trigger">Trigger</h2>
<p>The trigger will take action (e.g. send a notification) when the website does not return HTTP status code <code class="highlighter-rouge">200</code>.
On the hostâ€™s page, go to the <strong>Triggers</strong> tab and click on <em>Create trigger</em>:</p>

<p><img src="/files/zabbix-website-monitoring/trigger.png" alt="trigger.png" /></p>
<ul>
  <li><em>Name</em>: <code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;$WEBSITE_TITLE&gt;</code></li>
  <li><em>Severity</em>: <code class="highlighter-rouge">High</code></li>
  <li><em>Expression</em>: <code class="highlighter-rouge">{&lt;$HOST&gt;:web.test.error[&lt;$WEBSITE_TITLE&gt;].strlen()}&gt;0 and {&lt;$HOST&gt;:web.test.fail[&lt;$WEBSITE_TITLE&gt;].last()}&gt;0</code></li>
  <li><em>Allow manual close</em>: <code class="highlighter-rouge">x</code></li>
  <li><em>Enabled</em>: <code class="highlighter-rouge">x</code></li>
</ul>

<p>â€¦and click <em>Add</em>.</p>

